{"tid":2004102,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【國際戰線 免費文宣】記住每位手足嘅血汗 \"Wounds of Hong Kong\"","createTime":"2020-05-06T08:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T08:40:21.000Z","uid":281831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c74c5fa8fb2aa0dda9022232fbb51ddb19c6cbd9","tid":2004102,"uid":281831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">眾籌 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2WuNqw2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2WuNqw2&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBRfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=87a06baa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2WuNqw2</a> </span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得今年2月Sony World Photography Awards的主辦機構<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">World Photography Organisation(WPO)</span></strong>因為政治審查、把關於<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港抗爭者</span></span></strong>的參作品<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">下架</span></strong>嘅事？ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/art/抗爭者傷勢相-入圍-sony-世界攝影獎-港攝記高仲明-願更多人知道香港事/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fart%2F%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85%E5%82%B7%E5%8B%A2%E7%9B%B8-%E5%85%A5%E5%9C%8D-sony-%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E7%8D%8E-%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%9D%E8%A8%98%E9%AB%98%E4%BB%B2%E6%98%8E-%E9%A1%98%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%8B%2F&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBRfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=6dd4a503\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fart%2F%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85%E5%82%B7%E5%8B%A2%E7%9B%B8-%E5%85%A5%E5%9C%8D-sony-%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E7%8D%8E-%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%9D%E8%A8%98%E9%AB%98%E4%BB%B2%E6%98%8E-%E9%A1%98%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%8B%2F&h=e11cefdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/art/抗爭者傷勢相-入圍-sony-世界攝影獎-港攝記高仲明-願更多人知道香港事/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BoPkjxn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBoPkjxn.jpg&h=dbbb8462&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這輯相叫《Wounds of Hong Kong》 ，攝影師高仲明拍攝了24位受傷手足的照片，6月會出版一本中英雙語的相冊，以記錄警暴。照片和文字的版權完全開放，只要註明出處，人人均可採用，方便各位製作文宣。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">攬炒團隊Stand With Hong Kong（APPG）</span></strong></span>在提交英國國會的報告，已經率先採用。照片和文字會陸續在Facebook專頁post出來，以廣流傳。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/121484627866832/posts/3528089320539662/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F121484627866832%2Fposts%2F3528089320539662%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBRfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=dd2d7390\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/121484627866832/posts/3528089320539662/?d=n</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n現在<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">&quot; Wounds of Hong Kong&quot; </span></strong>正在眾籌，款項除了用作<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">印書</span></strong>，更重要是在世界各地<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">舉辦展覽</span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">以保持香港抗爭運動在國際社會的熱度</span></strong>。本來WPO這類國際比賽獲外媒轉載，是個理想的宣傳平台，得奬作品也會在世界各地巡迴展覽。但多得武漢肺炎&amp;<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">WPO舔共</span></strong>（10張相抽走左6張，因為「<span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭者的傷痕具煽動性</span>」，變成沒有&quot;Disappeared Wounds of Hong Kong&quot;），<span style=\"color: red;\">WPO</span>今年的展覽可能不了了之。所以我們決定：<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">自己展覽自己搞</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n香港的展覽在6月13日在<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">深水埗Openground</span></strong>舉行，為期3週。眾籌款項會用作海外展覽之用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VmqvGYK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVmqvGYK.jpg&h=bcb0eeb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UuJEAiL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUuJEAiL.jpg&h=d30cb840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P8E4Mqs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP8E4Mqs.jpg&h=b1ff748c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UTfGODO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUTfGODO.jpg&h=1b4b572c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ppWCmYP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FppWCmYP.jpg&h=ada23c5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54e342d665a44d7accb63084c8e05b8ee30d650f","tid":2004102,"uid":281831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:38:14.000Z","msg":"自推10次 x 1"},{"pid":"b569a501b51fcd629ed644b51e5987ac721aecd4","tid":2004102,"uid":281831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:38:30.000Z","msg":"自推10次 x 2"},{"pid":"608e558c7f5b7e292a92d49a8616f6fe671a387f","tid":2004102,"uid":281831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:38:53.000Z","msg":"自推10次 x 3"},{"pid":"8da1593ab796ae1f2b544d41d0723f3b46b9987a","tid":2004102,"uid":281831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:39:15.000Z","msg":"自推10次 x 4"},{"pid":"16c7d476c1f9c842d755e987705041c2e9ec7535","tid":2004102,"uid":281831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:39:25.000Z","msg":"自推10次 x 5"},{"pid":"13328aa1032fdad16a5abad1e08a73fbc30d475e","tid":2004102,"uid":281831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:39:35.000Z","msg":"自推10次 x 6"},{"pid":"9fdd03da10f45eb1fc77d2920585e02f957badcb","tid":2004102,"uid":281831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T08:39:48.00